## Summary

This documentation covers the `@supertokens-plugins/tenant-discovery-nodejs` plugin API reference, defining TypeScript type aliases for tenant discovery functionality including MinimalTenantDetails and OverrideableTenantFunctionImplementation, along with configuration types and exported functions for multi-tenant email-based tenant resolution.

